{"tid":2124814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[國際線手足] 匈牙利戰線要人 Twitter要人","createTime":"2020-07-25T16:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T16:24:13.000Z","uid":164430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a78b9f4186ae0732f0c1877baad9dcd0a27ced94","tid":2124814,"uid":164430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"話說前日(24號)匈牙利唯一嘅大型獨立新聞媒體<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">Index</span></span>嘅總編輯就俾董事局炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而匈牙利政府過去幾十年一直慢慢所有新聞媒體收編旗下<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>情況類似香港媒體<span class=\"red\">歸晒邊咁</span></strong></span><br />\n但佢地情況仲嚴重，宜家就得返呢間唔係政府／親政府商人係董事局話事，其餘就得返d細網媒咁<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">Index</span></span>個老總俾人炒左，所以班細嘅前日就集體辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲觸發左尋日民眾遊行去總理府抗議<br />\n<span class=\"small\">Source: <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53531948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-53531948&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=e6a5a17f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-53531948&h=10efa931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53531948</a></span><br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">Twitter要人！！！</span></span><br />\n即用 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">#IndexHu #nincsmasik</span></span> (得返一間咁解) 上Twitter retweet &amp; like 推po <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好俾人知道埋香港手足黎撐佢地啦～自己識做<br />\n<br />\n唔識？睇Twitter教學裝備自己！ <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1489008/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1489008/page/1</a>"}]}